Package com.googlecode.jaks.common.io

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EmptyInputStream
    An empty InputStream.
    FileUtil
    Static file utility methods.
    Filter  
    MultiOutputStream  
    NonClosingInputStream
    Aggregates an InputStream, overriding the NonClosingInputStream.close() method to prevent the consumer from explicitly closing the wrapped stream.
    NonClosingOutputStream
    Aggregates an OutputStream, overriding the NonClosingOutputStream.close() method to prevent the consumer from explicitly closing the wrapped stream (it calls NonClosingOutputStream.flush() instead).
    NonClosingReader
    Aggregates an Reader, overriding the NonClosingReader.close() method to prevent the consumer from explicitly closing the wrapped stream.
    NonClosingWriter
    Aggregates a Writer, overriding the NonClosingWriter.close() method to prevent the consumer from explicitly closing the wrapped stream (it calls NonClosingWriter.flush() instead).
    SquashedOutputStream
    OutputStream that squashes (ignores) the bytes written to it.
    StreamUtil
    Utility methods for InputStreams, OutputStreams, Readers, and Writers.
